{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0001", "text": "那一塊餅乾 仍能令你快樂到喫光", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 4, 9, 3, 0, 0, 2, 5, 4, 2, 4, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["naa5", "jat1", "faai3", "beng2", "gon1", "jing4", "nang4", "ling6", "nei5", "faai3", "lok6", "dou3", "hek3", "gwong1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一塊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "餅乾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "仍能", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "令", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快樂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喫光", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0002", "text": "你那容貌枯黃 但你", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 5, 0, 2, 3, 0, 2, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "naa5", "jung4", "maau6", "fu1", "wong4", "daan6", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "容貌", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "枯黃", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0003", "text": "不驚怕饑荒請我喫餅乾 淚差點要淌", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 4, 3, 3, 9, 5, 4, 9, 3, 2, 3, 9, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["bat1", "geng1", "paa3", "gei1", "fong1", "cing2", "ngo5", "hek3", "beng2", "gon1", "leoi6", "caa1", "dim2", "jiu3", "tong2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "驚怕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "饑荒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "請", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "餅乾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "淚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "差點", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "淌", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0004", "text": "偏僻高原遍地茫最矜貴 志願原來是上堂", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 3, 3, 0, 4, 2, 0, 4, 3, 4, 4, 2, 0, 0, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["pin1", "pik1", "gou1", "jyun4", "pin3", "dei6", "mong4", "zeoi3", "ging1", "gwai3", "zi3", "jyun6", "jyun4", "loi4", "si6", "tong4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "偏僻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "高原", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "遍地", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "茫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "矜貴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "志願", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "原來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "上堂", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0005", "text": "你說你學懂講晚安 希望有塊厚墊當牀", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 5, 2, 9, 9, 5, 3, 3, 2, 5, 4, 5, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "syut3", "nei5", "hok6", "dung2", "gong2", "maan5", "on1", "hei1", "mong6", "jau5", "faai3", "hau5", "din3", "cong4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "學懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "晚安", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "希望", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "有塊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "厚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "墊", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "當牀", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0006", "text": "但最嚮往 看雨滴到訪", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 9}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 4, 5, 4, 5, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daan6", "zeoi3", "hoeng3", "wong5", "hon3", "jyu5", "dik1", "dou3", "fong2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "最", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "嚮往", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "看", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "雨滴", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "到訪", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0007", "text": "天涯長萬里 一轉身已經遠離", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 0, 0, 2, 5, 3, 9, 3, 5, 3, 5, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["tin1", "ngaai4", "coeng4", "maan6", "lei5", "jat1", "zyun2", "san1", "ji5", "ging1", "jyun5", "lei4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "天涯", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "長", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "萬里", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "轉身", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已經", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "遠離", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0008", "text": "踏遍這地球繁華絕美 但未曾忘記你", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 4, 5, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 5, 2, 2, 0, 0, 4, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["daap6", "pin3", "ze5", "dei6", "kau4", "faan4", "waa4", "zyut6", "mei5", "daan6", "mei6", "cang4", "mong4", "gei3", "nei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "踏遍", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "地球", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "繁華", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "絕美", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "但", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "未曾", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "忘記", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0009", "text": "天才難及你 不必懂誰是誰非", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 12}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [3, 0, 0, 2, 5, 3, 3, 9, 0, 2, 0, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["tin1", "coi4", "naan4", "kap6", "nei5", "bat1", "bit1", "dung2", "seoi4", "si6", "seoi4", "fei1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "天才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難及", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不必", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "懂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰是誰非", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0010", "text": "每日要爲 進食皺眉", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 8}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 2, 4, 4, 2, 4, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mui5", "jat6", "jiu3", "zeon3", "sik6", "zau3", "mei4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "每日", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "爲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "進食", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "皺眉", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0011", "text": "無智慧去探索天理 才窮得悽美", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 4, 2, 4, 4, 4, 3, 5, 0, 0, 3, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["mou4", "zi3", "wai6", "heoi3", "taam3", "sok3", "tin1", "lei5", "coi4", "kung4", "dak1", "cai1", "mei5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "無", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "智慧", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "去", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "探索", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天理", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "才", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "窮", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "得", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "悽美", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0012", "text": "你真正纖瘦 謎城內女仕誰是你對手", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 4, 3, 4, 0, 0, 2, 5, 2, 0, 2, 5, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "zan1", "zing3", "cim1", "sau3", "mai4", "sing4", "noi6", "neoi5", "si6", "seoi4", "si6", "nei5", "deoi3", "sau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真正", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "纖瘦", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "謎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "城內", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "女仕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "誰", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對手", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0013", "text": "你說我是否要走", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 7}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 4, 5, 2, 9, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["nei5", "syut3", "ngo5", "si6", "fau2", "jiu3", "zau2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "是否", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "要", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "走", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "請我喫餅乾", "artists": ["梁詠琪"], "lyricists": ["林夕"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_1797", "prev_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_5qKB5ZKP55Cq_MTc5Nw_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
